to me in conversation,

51
00:05:14,150 --> 00:05:16,125
not in the confessional.

52
00:05:16,175 --> 00:05:20,000
Which means I'm not breaking
the seal of confession.

53
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:21,525
What are you about to tell me?

54
00:05:21,575 --> 00:05:25,950
The Pope is going through
a profound crisis of faith.

55
00:05:26,450 --> 00:05:30,125
What are you insinuating,
Don Tommaso?

56
00:05:30,175 --> 00:05:33,925
That the Pope
doesn't believe in God.

57
00:07:24,450 --> 00:07:27,150
They've manifested themselves.

58
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:30,175
Who?

59
00:07:32,325 --> 00:07:34,250
My Mom and Dad.

60
00:07:35,175 --> 00:07:37,050
But how?

61
00:07:38,875 --> 00:07:42,400
It came in a box.
No postmark, no nothing.

62
00:07:42,450 --> 00:07:45,575
Not a clue,
no way to track them down.

63
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:50,875
