that gets our Church
back on course,

76
00:10:46,325 --> 00:10:48,800
this would be the right time
to do it.

77
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:53,125
I've done my part.
Now you need to do yours.

78
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:58,275
What exactly have you done?

79
00:10:58,325 --> 00:11:00,650
You'd better be ready, Voiello.

80
00:11:09,300 --> 00:11:11,200
Someone might see us.

81
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:32,500
There is a new preface by Joseph.

82
00:11:33,925 --> 00:11:35,650
I'm depressed, Angelo.

83
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:38,250
I don't give a shit
that you're depressed, Michael.

84
00:11:38,300 --> 00:11:41,075
At night, I take care
of a disabled boy.

85
00:11:41,125 --> 00:11:43,950
Last night I was looking at him,

86
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:48,650
he was drooling and his eyes were
blank, and I thought to myself:

87
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:51,500
what is the Church
doing for this boy?

88
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,375
And the answer was simple:

89
00:11:53,425 --> 00:11:55,875
the Church is doing nothing.

90
00:11:55,925 --> 00:11:57,075
Why?

91
00:11:57,125 --> 00:12:00,250
What was it doing before Pius XIII?

92
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:03,200
Are you depressed or suffering
from amnesia, Michael?

93
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:07,125
Before Pius XIII the Church
was taking care of the poor.

94
00:12:07,175 --> 00:12:10,150
It was "also" taking care
of the poor.

95
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:12,150
But there's a bigger question.

96
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:15,775
What is the Church doing
on a more general basis?

97
00:12:15,825 --> 00:12:18,075
It's not doing anything anymore.

98
00:12:18,125 --> 00:12:19,850
It's killing time.

99
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:22,325
We have a Church
that's just killing time

100
00:12:22,825 --> 00:12:24,975
and has become infinitely marginal.

101
00:12:25,025 --> 00:12:28,825
That's exactly what the Pope wants:
a marginal Church.

102
00:12:28,875 --> 00:12:31,200
Small and dead.

103
00:12:31,250 --> 00:12:34,275
He said it and now he's done it.

104
00:12:34,325 --> 00:12:36,700
He wants to take the Church
back to its beginnings?

105
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:40,200
In the beginning, all this was
nothing more than Peter's tomb.

106
00:12:40,250 --> 00:12:42,525
For what purpose?

107
00:12:42,575 --> 00:12:44,875
To close himself off,
to deny himself,

108
00:12:44,925 --> 00:12:48,275
to make himself inaccessible
and mysterious?

109
00:12:48,325 --> 00:12:52,050
Sacrifice and suffering
to get closer to God.

110
00:12:52,625 --> 00:12:57,125
In his convoluted logic this
strategy is supposed to stimulate

111
