Fine!
But none of this is happening.

114
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:10,275
The churches are empty.

115
00:13:10,325 --> 00:13:14,450
The mass with the Tridentine rite
would discourage anyone.

116
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:19,400
It's now harder to become a priest
than it is to become an astronaut.

117
00:13:19,450 --> 00:13:22,500
The Pope is refusing to refinance
the missions.

118
00:13:22,550 --> 00:13:26,250
Our non-relations with other
religions are tense and dangerous.

119
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:31,100
We've become few in number, alone,
against the rest of the world.

120
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:34,850
St. Peter's Square is empty,
dreary, and abandoned.

121
00:13:35,450 --> 00:13:38,575
Michael, we have the duty
to take steps.

122
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:41,750
How?

123
00:13:51,950 --> 00:13:54,800
Michael, come see.

124
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:20,125
I know how to get him to resign,
Michael.

125
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:32,875
And who would this new Pope be?

126
00:15:28,575 --> 00:15:33,275
Forgive me, Lord, for
I have deceived, I am deceiving,

127
00:15:33,325 --> 00:15:37,775
and I will continue to deceive
the Holy Father.

128
00:15:37,825 --> 00:15:40,075
Forgive me, Lord,

129
00:15:40,125 --> 00:15:43,650
but I can no longer continue
to look on at the destruction

130
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:47,950
of the man I love
more than I love myself.

131
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:50,575
Forgive me, Lord,

132
00:15:50,625 --> 00:15:54,625
for I cannot continue any longer
to look on at the destruction

133
00:15:54,675 --> 00:15:59,050
of the institution I love
more than I love myself:

134
00:16:00,625 --> 00:16:03,950
the holy Roman Church.

135
00:16:27,825 --> 00:16:31,175
- Having fun, Aldo?
- Yeah, I guess...

136
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:00,000
Don't you agree it's a crime

137
00:17:00,050 --> 00:17:03,825
