is in decline, Your Eminence?

138
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:12,400
Is it really such a bad thing?

139
00:17:12,450 --> 00:17:14,000
I should say so.

140
00:17:14,050 --> 00:17:18,250
My father taught me the art of the
cocktail when I was twenty-five.

141
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:20,750
My father was one
of the first people in Italy

142
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:24,375
